-------------------------
gnome-voice-control 0.3.0
-------------------------

New features and UI improvements:

    * Port to pocketsphinx, much faster now with wsj model.
    * Libnotify support.
    * New actions for clicks, keyboard and main menu.
    
Thanks:

    David Huggins-Daines
    Marius Andreiana

Translators:

    Olivier Blanc (fr)

